Title: Autumn Memories
Writer: Ali Fakhr Mousavi, Kateryna Turchanikova, Viktor Vilhelm
Actors: Nazanin Ahmady Sshahpour Abady, Aleksandr Ignatusha, Galyna Karpin, Oleksa Kravchuk
Plot: Ukrainian sculptor who is taking wife's death hard acquires the hope to begin a new life after appearance of Iraqi refugee. He desires to fall in love not taking into consideration the rival of young soldier.
